<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark">
            <div class="container-fluid">
                <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">
                    <img src="/images/placeholder.png" alt="Logo" class="logo">
                </a>
                <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbarNav" aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                    <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
                </button>
                <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                    <ul class="navbar-nav ml-auto">
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="/">Home</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="#community">Community</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="#search">The Search</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="/login">Sign Up</a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>


    <div id="hero-carousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="false">
        <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item active">
                <section class="hero slide1">
                    <div class="content">
                        <h1>The Purdue community has been rattled by the sudden disappearance of Professor Xander, director of the PEARL Lab.</h1>
                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-warning">JOIN THE HUNT</a>
                    </div>
                </section>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <section class="hero slide2">
                    <div class="content">
                        <h1>Follow the clues and piece together the mystery of Professor Xander's disappearance and the future of AI at Purdue.</h1>
                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-warning">EXPLORE LAB</a>
                    </div>
                </section>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <section class="hero slide3">
                    <div class="content">
                        <h1>Envision the future of Purdue with AI integrated across campus transforming education and Purdue itself.</h1>
                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-warning">VIEW COMMUNITY</a>
                    </div>
                </section>
            </div>
        </div>
        <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#hero-carousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
        </a>
        <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#hero-carousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
        </a>
    </div>


    <section id="community" class="community py-5 bg-dark">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="text-center mb-4">Community</h2>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card bg-secondary mb-4">
                        <div class="card-body text-center">
                            <h3>Re-Imagining Purdue</h3>
                            <p>Check out Tomorrow's Purdue: With AI, a creative showcase, where you will find a stunning array of AI-generated images that re-imagine our Purdue campus in imaginative and innovative ways.</p>
                            <a href="#" class="btn btn-warning">View more</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card bg-secondary mb-4">
                        <div class="card-body text-center">
                            <h3>AI-Enabled Solutions</h3>
                            <p>Check out the realm of visionary solutions for the future of education and campus life! Explore identified problems and innovative solutions and join in shaping Purdueâ€™s future.</p>
                            <a href="#" class="btn btn-warning">View more</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card bg-secondary mb-4">
                        <div class="card-body text-center">
                            <h3>Perceptions About AI</h3>
                            <p>Navigate through this interactive space where the diverse perspectives of players converge to shape the understanding of AI.</p>
                            <a href="#" class="btn btn-warning">View more</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="research" class="research-section py-5 bg-dark">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="card bg-secondary mb-4">
                        <div class="card-body text-center">
                            <h3>Research Lab</h3>
                            <p>Purdue University's AI Lab stands at the forefront of innovation, spearheading advancements in artificial intelligence (AI) to address complex challenges.</p>
                            <a href="#" class="btn btn-warning">View more</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="card bg-secondary mb-4">
                        <div class="card-body text-center">
                            <h3>Dr. Emily Xander</h3>
                            <p>Dr. Emily Xander's early career was marked by significant contributions to AI research, including advanced learning algorithms and natural language processing. Over the years, her interests...</p>
                            <a href="#" class="btn btn-warning">View more</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <% if (!user) { %>
        <div class="sticky-bar">
            <span>Join the hunt and help solve the mystery of Professor Emma Thompson's disappearance!</span>
            <a href="/auth/google" class="btn btn-primary">Sign Up</a>
        </div>
    <% } %>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.9.3/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
